,"uid":229653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T18:02:47.000Z","msg":"踢春袋啦講咁多"},{"pid":"6266846d20a8c3aff238df0b027c9de78a994162","tid":1606253,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59af5a652da1812c9f55250fbdd3b44153fb329e","tid":1606253,"uid":229653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T18:02:47.000Z","msg":"踢春袋啦講咁多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T18:20:04.000Z","msg":"肯定有護陰架喎<br />\n你對跑鞋硬D定護陰硬D?<br />\n腳踢唔踢到百幾磅力?"},{"pid":"8722ef3e6d4e6a16d6f8451c4f043a6b548af9d4","tid":1606253,"uid":201678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T18:33:43.000Z","msg":"一人一磚係要個震攝力<br />\n<br />\n要令班黑警唔敢再行前半步<br />\n<br />\n極重要 古羅馬野史  請求各位朋友聽下個故事 純歷史分享 求推熱門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"04d6f0f785a4ff02ea31cb8d3fc3175fb1d94aba","tid":1606253,"uid":282134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T18:39:35.000Z","msg":"揾野墊住佢隻腳 再踩落波羅蓋"},{"pid":"2c2625979add1cda7b5e9a229d4f04b2e14d06c2","tid":1606253,"uid":282134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04d6f0f785a4ff02ea31cb8d3fc3175fb1d94aba","tid":1606253,"uid":282134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T18:39:35.000Z","msg":"揾野墊住佢隻腳 再踩落波羅蓋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T18:41:12.000Z","msg":"拉高佢隻腳可以考慮將佢打側先 再踩側面菠蘿蓋 佢護腳多數包前後"},{"pid":"56d2a96c1c0f95a269516e49d9ea5e429412cbb5","tid":1606253,"uid":34241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T18:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72562f51ed672be8f3764c7a7aa2e1eccedd3f9","tid":1606253,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:29:23.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n出發前睇睇"},{"pid":"0ad9f6edc8e553b5699b9c115d05fda901738c0b","tid":1606253,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b15b2d0bd344dcb685edf4e34978c991ff98f0","tid":1606253,"uid":3524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T21:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9408fb452137cf921ffe244497b3d85b6eab8c3f","tid":1606253,"uid":3524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T21:04:50.000Z","msg":"好堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}